window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The first three action-packed episodes of the best-selling America Falls series: <br> <i>Hell Week</i>,<i> On the Run</i>, and <i>Cold Comfort</i>.&nbsp;</p> <p>No mazes. No zombies. No games.&nbsp;</p> <p>If you think North Korea and Russia are the greatest dangers to the US - think again. After a surprise biological attack, America, the most powerful nation on earth, quickly succumbs, with more than 99.5 percent of the adult population killed. As society unravels and a ground invasion of his country begins, loner Isaac Race must form a connection with a ragtag group of survivors and elude not only the invaders, but other dangers and chaos unleashed in Post-America.</p> <p>These are the first three episodes of America Falls, a compelling, action-packed story about who we are and who we have to become in order to survive.</p> <p>Buy the bundle and start a series you wonâ€™t want to put down!&nbsp;</p>"; 
